{{#> layout}}
    <h2>Welcome to Mobile Banking!</h2>
    
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for choosing Mobile Banking. We're excited to have you on board! Your account has been successfully created and is ready to use.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <p><strong>Getting Started:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Download our mobile app</li>
            <li>Set up your security preferences</li>
            <li>Add your favorite billers</li>
            <li>Explore our banking features</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>To access your account, click the button below:</p>
    
    <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>

    <p>For your security, we recommend:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Use a strong, unique password</li>
        <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
        <li>Never share your login credentials</li>
        <li>Always log out when finished</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is available 24/7.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> If you didn't create this account, please contact us immediately.</p>
    </div>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Mobile Banking Team</p>
{{/layout}}
